# App Updates Implementation Plan

## User Review Required
> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Biometric Logic Change**: To fix the infinite FaceID loop, I will disable the automatic authentication check in [main.dart](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/Aniruddh/Extracurricular/flutter-app/the_30sec_journal/lib/main.dart) that runs every time the app resumes. Instead, authentication will be strictly handled by the [AuthWrapper](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/Aniruddh/Extracurricular/flutter-app/the_30sec_journal/lib/screens/auth_wrapper.dart#14-19) on startup and `SettingsScreen` for toggling. This prevents the loop caused by system dialogs interfering with app lifecycle states.

