### Feature: Bug Fixes

#### [MODIFY] [audio_player_widget.dart](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/Aniruddh/Extracurricular/flutter-app/the_30sec_journal/lib/widgets/audio_player_widget.dart)
- Fix [_initSource](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/Aniruddh/Extracurricular/flutter-app/the_30sec_journal/lib/widgets/audio_player_widget.dart#52-59): Ensure `getDuration` is called after setting the source so `_duration` is not zero.
- Improve [_formatDuration](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/Aniruddh/Extracurricular/flutter-app/the_30sec_journal/lib/widgets/audio_player_widget.dart#66-76) to handle edge cases.

#### [MODIFY] [calendar_screen.dart](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/Aniruddh/Extracurricular/flutter-app/the_30sec_journal/lib/screens/calendar_screen.dart)
- Update `TableCalendar` `lastDay` to `DateTime.now()` to prevent future selection.
- Add check in [onDaySelected](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/Aniruddh/Extracurricular/flutter-app/the_30sec_journal/lib/screens/calendar_screen.dart#36-43) to ignore future dates.

#### [MODIFY] [main.dart](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/Aniruddh/Extracurricular/flutter-app/the_30sec_journal/lib/main.dart)
- **Remove** or **Refine** [didChangeAppLifecycleState](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/Aniruddh/Extracurricular/flutter-app/the_30sec_journal/lib/main.dart#61-66) logic. The loop happens because [_checkBiometrics](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/Aniruddh/Extracurricular/flutter-app/the_30sec_journal/lib/main.dart#67-85) triggers a system dialog -> app resigns active -> app resumes -> triggers [_checkBiometrics](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/Aniruddh/Extracurricular/flutter-app/the_30sec_journal/lib/main.dart#67-85) again.
- Removing the resume check is the safest way to fix the loop while keeping startup security in [AuthWrapper](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/Aniruddh/Extracurricular/flutter-app/the_30sec_journal/lib/screens/auth_wrapper.dart#14-19).

#### [MODIFY] [auth_wrapper.dart](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/Aniruddh/Extracurricular/flutter-app/the_30sec_journal/lib/screens/auth_wrapper.dart)
- Ensure [_authenticate](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/Aniruddh/Extracurricular/flutter-app/the_30sec_journal/lib/screens/auth_wrapper.dart#56-64) properly sets `_isLocked` state.

